caption: Gyro was tasty and my husbands pizza was fresh and hot.
Been getting food here since high school. The family that runs this place are so sweet. The food is always hot and top notch stuff. Highly recommend

We have been getting the white pizza with garlic and spinach, OMG sofa king good! I even eat the crust! My son gets pineapple, olive, chicken. I had a bite of that and it was great as well! We will continue to order from Georgia’s at least once a week for our family while in Salem! We always look forward to Georgia’s Pizza night now!
Friendly staff.
Wings bomb. Pizza bomb. Broccoli bites bomb. Quick  delivery service. I would give this place 20 stars. Great service all the way around. Food was piping hot when we got it too.
Consistently good food, I always call here when I don't want to cook
I love Georgia's food and great service
Great food, friendly and warm family atmosphere.  I love this place ❤
Have been ordering from them for almost 10 years, no lie! Quality, delicious food and such friendly staff. This family-owned restaurant is one of my top favorite restaurants in Salem.

I’ve been getting pizza here for years. I’ve never been unsatisfied. Food is always fresh, the family that own this place are so nice and wonderful. I will always get food from here first if I’m craving pizza!
Great pizza and a wonderful woman behind the counter I will be returning every time I come to Salem

Stumbled upon this place just by chance. Ordered a hot Italian sub and we were blown away. It was so simple and yet so good, nothing fancy just perfection. Husband said one of the best he’s ever had. Owner was so kind and said she put’s love into everything she makes and you can tell. Thanks for the best sub we had on the East coast.
It’s my go-to place when I eat out.  Whether it’s pizza, a sub, a beef sammich with broccoli bites, it’s always good.
Twice in 24 hours good!   New to Salem, glad I found this place.  So good!

I love this place. The staff is AMAZING, the food is CONSISTENTLY AMAZING, they accommodate all requests. Was ordering something from here that wasn’t even on the menu for a while and realized they were just making it happen for me. Love em. Best pizza in Salem.

Surely a place worth stopping over, the food is awesome and fresh, the prices are affordable and it is always neat here. Highly recommended.
I love it
Excellent food and friendly service
Great service and delicious Greek style pizza order 1 or 2 times a week
The best steak and cheese calzone! My boyfriend always stops in on the weekends and we eat the whole pie throughout the 🌙!!! Very friendly owners also. Definitely Recommend!!!
The best pizza and customer service.  LOVELY  LADY
Popped in for a slice. Hot and yummy!!
Coming from New York pizza was great! Very cozy place and extremely friendly staff.

Excellent pizza, thin crust and amazing sauce. Small place with a few stools and counter. Easy order and carry out. Georgia, the owner, was a delight to meet. Don’t pass by this pizzeria. Glad we found you!
Good pizza, fresh and very good steak and cheese sub!  This is a convenient take out place and cheap eats In Salem
Staff is cool... its cheap.. and its reflected in the food... saves my life when broke though.
Tasty pizza, crisp crust nice tangy sauce. Nice family shop
Nice people. Friendly, good food. Pizza by the slice, downtown Salem.
Had a really nice big cheese steak, reasonably priced
Great food & superior service. My go to favorite restaurant, especially kind delivery!!
Great food, I love there chicken salad subs
My all time favorite pizza, sub and salad place in the whole town of Salem. A tight-knit family owned restaurant that is consistent with quality food and customer service! Violet is the best!
Great food, cheap, large sizes, great family.
Friendly staff, clean establishment, great food
Their food is amazing!
Love these people! And great food!

The people are very nice , they remember your name. There food is good. There kinda slow delivering but I think it’s only one person delivering the product. So saying that I think they should hire more delivery drivers for they can have all around good service.
Love the staff.sincerely friendly.Good steak and cheese
Chicken salad is the best

My husband and I stopped in for a quick bite (a few slices) before a tour in Salem. The staff was friendly, the food came out quickly and our pizza was DELICIOUS. Worth the walk off the main road in Salem!
Friendly clean and the pizza is amazing not one ounce of grease under the crust in the crust was so crispy and thin oh my God I enjoyed it
Had the steak calzone, and it was heaven. Everything is made fresh and the people are very nice.
Super friendly and welcoming! Great food too!

Pizzas are made fresh, so they take a little bit of time to be ready. Food tastes great and the prices are pretty good. The shop is pretty small, so there isn't much seating and there isn't any ourdoor seating other than a area down the street. A good place to get pizza if you're taking it somewhere else.
Quick service, great food.

Great food reasonable prices, family owned nice people.

We were tired after traveling and learned about this on the internet.  We did take out. My husband had the chicken kabobs and rice and I had a chicken kabob salad. We also had soup. Delicious, hot food!  Recommend Georgia's Pizza...
Friendly pizza and sub joint. Good food, reasonably priced. Has small lunch counter. The tourists never find there way here, but they should!
Good food nice people
Good salad. Attentive service
Friendly,  accommodating and REALLY good food.  A hidden treasure
Really enjoyed my lunch staff was amazingly  friendly and accommodating Gyro was delicious!!! And free parking!!! Next visit to Salem U can bet I'll be back. Thanks!!!
Great people and food. I have been ordering there for over 8 years amd have bothnng but good things to say...

I love this place I go here often and always get delivery servcie when asked what what the best place to go for great food in Salem I highly recommend them to go here I would not know what to do if this place didn't exist I love the Italian calazone the Italian subs the pizza is way better then these new places and much better then engine house I appreciate all you do for the the city in providing great place to eat keep up the Good work .
Great pizza, great price, and super friendly Albanian staff!
Incredibly  nice people  very friendly  lots of integrity. And great food as well
The food is pretty good but last time I went I had sum horrible service.
Best pizza we have had in a while. Awesome service and very friendly.

Friendly people, but make a pretty lousy sub. Did not toast even though requested. My soda was expired, no excuse for that from such a small shop. Somehow a $6.30 sub and a 20oz was $9.70 after tax, so that 20oz soda must have been close to $3.

These guys are great, the nicest people always can take a last minute order, they always deliver the food with a smile and are grateful to do business with you. It helps their food is great and the prices are low compared to most other pizza shops.
The calzones at Georgia's are the best!!!
You like pizza???? Order from Georgia's! Trust me, you will not regret it.

While wondering around Salem looking for pizza as everything else was closed, We stumbled upon Georgia's pizza, a little location that you'd easily miss if you weren't looking for it (located by the 7-11 and Hong Kong Chinese food).The pizza was absolutely amazing and the service was great and fast, highly recommended!

As a New Yorker, my standards for pizza are pretty high. This cute little shop tucked away in a corner less than five minutes walking from my hotel has some of the best pizza I've ever had. Great pizza at good prices. We walked in during closing at the end of our guided tour hoping to snag a quick snack, and they made us a huge thing of spaghetti and threw in a free slice of pizza! I've never had such great service from a pizzeria. Extremely recommended.

We got pizza here while in Salem and it was REALLY good. I was not expecting how awesome it tasted. The driver was really nice, too!  I am marking decor as excellent, but I don't really know as it was delivered.
The cheesesteak calzone is wicked good!!! The best place around violet rocks!!
